Have a seat.

1056
01:22:17,380 --> 01:22:18,984
So, the picture.

1057
01:22:19,048 --> 01:22:20,152
Um...

1058
01:22:21,217 --> 01:22:23,219
I've been working with Adam Lang 
on his memoirs.

1059
01:22:23,286 --> 01:22:25,357
Yes, I know, you told me.

1060
01:22:25,922 --> 01:22:30,268
Yes, poor Lang. it's bad business, 
this posturing by The Hague.

1061
01:22:30,827 --> 01:22:34,172
As for Rycart, the worst 
British Foreign Secretary since the war.

1062
01:22:34,230 --> 01:22:35,368
Lang was right to fire him.

1063
01:22:35,431 --> 01:22:38,310
-How well do you know Lang? 
-Hardly at all.

1064
01:22:39,502 --> 01:22:42,813
-You seem surprised. 
-He mentions you in his memoirs.

1065
01:22:42,872 --> 01:22:44,146
Oh, really?

1066
01:22:45,174 --> 01:22:49,589
Well, now it's my turn to be surprised. 
What does he say?

1067
